premise_source_doc_sentence: She is known for her role as Donna Pinciotti in all eight seasons of the Fox sitcom That '70s Show  (  1998 -- 2006  )  , and for her role as Alex Vause in the Netflix original comedy-drama series Orange Is the New Black  (  2013 -- present  )  .
That '80s Show is an American sitcom that aired from January through May 2002 .

Although the main character , Corey Howard  (  Glenn Howerton  )  , is designed as Eric Forman 's  (  Topher Grace  )  cousin , the show itself was a separate decade-based show created because of That '70s Show '' 's popularity at the time .
Despite having a similar name , show structure , and many of the same writers and production staff , it is not considered a direct-sequel of the more successful That '70s Show .
On November 3 , 2015 , Mill Creek released That '70s Show - The Complete Series on Blu-ray for the very first time .
